00:00:36.086 --> 00:00:37.003 line:90%
Gu-cheon!

00:00:37.087 --> 00:00:38.421 line:90%
Gu-cheon!

00:00:39.589 --> 00:00:41.508 line:90%
Please come to your senses.

00:00:42.092 --> 00:00:43.093 line:90%
Gu-cheon!

00:00:54.604 --> 00:00:55.939 line:90%
Are you all right?

00:00:59.734 --> 00:01:01.361 line:90%
Gu-cheon.

00:01:49.242 --> 00:01:54.164 line:90%
THE EAST PALACE

00:01:54.748 --> 00:01:59.711 line:90%
So you drove out 13 court ladies' spirits
in the salt storehouse?

00:02:02.756 --> 00:02:04.299 line:90%
You have done well.

00:02:04.382 --> 00:02:05.425 line:90%
You may withdraw.

00:02:05.926 --> 00:02:07.510 line:90%
I have something to ask you.

00:02:08.428 --> 00:02:11.181 line:90%
Did you have anything to do
with the broken seal

00:02:11.264 --> 00:02:12.849 line:90%
on the salt storehouse?

00:02:13.350 --> 00:02:14.851 line:90%
You have changed,

00:02:14.935 --> 00:02:18.730 line:90%
to dare ask such a thing now.

00:02:19.689 --> 00:02:20.815 line:90%
But as a child,

00:02:21.316 --> 00:02:26.071 line:90%
you must have seen how such words
led to bloodshed upon the palace.

00:02:26.154 --> 00:02:27.739 line:90%
You saw what befell your mother.

00:02:27.822 --> 00:02:30.200 line:90%
"I will wipe out every last seed
of the East Palace."

00:02:30.951 --> 00:02:33.954 line:90%
The Most Favored Lady of the Court
who died in the pond said this.

00:02:34.663 --> 00:02:36.498 line:90%
She is the pond spirit, is she not?

00:02:36.581 --> 00:02:37.916 line:90%
Who exactly is she?

00:02:37.999 --> 00:02:40.377 line:90%
What led to her death?

00:02:43.672 --> 00:02:46.591 line:90%
Are you the only one who knows of this,

00:02:46.675 --> 00:02:49.094 line:90%
or does Gu-cheon know as well?

00:02:50.553 --> 00:02:51.680 line:90%
I'm the only one who knows.

00:02:56.977 --> 00:02:59.020 line:90%
Do not tell him anything.

00:02:59.521 --> 00:03:03.316 line:90%
To capture the pond spirit,
I need to know who she was in life.

00:03:05.568 --> 00:03:07.904 line:90%
I will say this one last time.

00:03:09.114 --> 00:03:11.032 line:90%
Do not try to learn about the pond spirit.

00:03:11.116 --> 00:03:13.535 line:90%
You can catch it
without knowing its identity.

00:03:13.618 --> 00:03:15.954 line:90%
Do not look further into it.

00:03:16.913 --> 00:03:20.000 line:90%
Anyone who pries into shameful secrets
of the palace will die.

00:03:20.083 --> 00:03:21.126 line:90%
Even

00:03:22.502 --> 00:03:24.671 line:90%
a child of the royal bloodline.

00:03:37.934 --> 00:03:39.853 line:90%
Are you still unwell?

00:03:41.062 --> 00:03:43.314 line:90%
You are healing more slowly
than last time.

00:03:43.398 --> 00:03:49.863 line:90%
Sending 13 spirits back to the afterlife
drained my Yang energy.

00:03:50.530 --> 00:03:52.949 line:90%
I will never do this again.

00:03:54.325 --> 00:03:57.287 line:90%
Very well. So tell me now.

00:03:58.413 --> 00:03:59.873 line:90%
Why did you strangle me?

00:04:07.714 --> 00:04:08.923 line:90%
I did?

00:04:09.507 --> 00:04:11.551 line:90%
Yes. You looked

00:04:12.719 --> 00:04:14.345 line:90%
just like a spirit.

00:04:25.899 --> 00:04:27.442 line:90%
In the Realm of Gwi…

00:04:31.321 --> 00:04:34.074 line:90%
I lose Yang energy
every time I fight spirits.

00:04:36.701 --> 00:04:39.079 line:90%
Sometimes, I lose too much Yang energy

00:04:39.871 --> 00:04:43.041 line:90%
and become like a spirit
even out of the water.

00:04:44.959 --> 00:04:48.671 line:90%
It means I sometimes lose control
and do not know what I might do.

00:04:51.591 --> 00:04:54.094 line:90%
That is why I want to leave
the palace at once.

00:04:55.929 --> 00:04:57.222 line:90%
And that is the reason

00:04:57.806 --> 00:05:00.058 line:90%
I hate hunting spirits.

00:05:08.608 --> 00:05:09.567 line:90%
Well…

00:05:12.445 --> 00:05:15.073 line:90%
now that I have told you my secret,

00:05:16.366 --> 00:05:17.534 line:90%
you should

00:05:18.660 --> 00:05:20.578 line:90%
tell me what is on your mind.

00:05:21.121 --> 00:05:23.581 line:90%
Who is it that you want to kill
in the palace?

00:05:25.875 --> 00:05:27.919 line:90%
The one who killed my mother.

00:05:31.339 --> 00:05:35.218 line:90%
A cursed object containing human remains
was found in the salt storehouse.

00:05:36.427 --> 00:05:37.887 line:90%
Since you bore only a princess,

00:05:37.971 --> 00:05:40.348 line:90%
His Majesty has not set foot
in your chambers.

00:05:40.431 --> 00:05:44.686 line:90%
And out of jealousy, you cursed the Queen
and the other concubines, did you?

00:05:45.186 --> 00:05:46.271 line:90%
That is not true.

00:05:49.065 --> 00:05:52.986 line:90%
That cursed object was not my doing.

00:05:53.069 --> 00:05:54.320 line:90%
Enough.

00:05:54.404 --> 00:05:55.989 line:90%
This is your doing.

00:05:58.992 --> 00:05:59.951 line:90%
Continue.

00:06:00.034 --> 00:06:01.953 line:90%
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

00:06:04.414 --> 00:06:05.623 line:90%
<i>It was ten years ago.</i>

00:06:06.332 --> 00:06:10.378 line:90%
<i>Her Majesty the Queen Dowager</i>
<i>framed my mother and drove her out.</i>

00:06:10.962 --> 00:06:12.797 line:90%
Father, please help.

00:06:13.381 --> 00:06:15.592 line:90%
Please stop Her Majesty the Queen Dowager.

00:06:15.675 --> 00:06:18.720 line:90%
Mother and the court ladies are innocent.

00:06:19.220 --> 00:06:23.391 line:90%
-It was because I heard strange things--
-Enough.

00:06:24.017 --> 00:06:26.519 line:90%
I will strip your mother of her title
and cast her out

00:06:26.603 --> 00:06:28.146 line:90%
for burying the cursed object.

00:06:28.646 --> 00:06:30.440 line:90%
That is her only way to survive.

00:06:30.523 --> 00:06:33.318 line:90%
But that cursed object
does not belong to Mother.

00:06:33.902 --> 00:06:37.989 line:90%
The spirits in the salt storehouse said,
"The serpent's cast skin killed--"

00:06:39.532 --> 00:06:41.492 line:90%
Hold your tongue.

00:06:42.911 --> 00:06:47.248 line:90%
Do not say
that my own child hears such things.

00:06:47.332 --> 00:06:50.001 line:90%
Unless you mean to disgrace
the royal house.

00:06:51.127 --> 00:06:54.547 line:90%
Do not tell anyone. Anyone at all.

00:06:55.506 --> 00:06:57.133 line:90%
Ever.

00:07:01.346 --> 00:07:02.722 line:90%
How foolish.

00:07:06.935 --> 00:07:08.603 line:90%
Utterly foolish.

00:07:09.938 --> 00:07:13.191 line:90%
You must always mind your words
in the palace.

00:07:31.668 --> 00:07:34.420 line:90%
Follow your mother and leave the palace!

00:07:37.966 --> 00:07:39.384 line:90%
Father.

00:07:40.134 --> 00:07:41.427 line:90%
How could you…

00:07:54.148 --> 00:07:56.234 line:90%
<i>After we were cast out of the palace,</i>

00:07:57.485 --> 00:07:59.570 line:90%
<i>Mother was poisoned to death…</i>

00:08:02.699 --> 00:08:04.742 line:90%
<i>because she found the cursed object</i>

00:08:05.243 --> 00:08:07.662 line:90%
<i>and came close</i>
<i>to the secret of the pond spirit.</i>

00:08:08.871 --> 00:08:12.500 line:90%
Someone killed my mother
to protect the secret of the pond spirit.

00:08:15.253 --> 00:08:20.133 line:90%
-Are you sure you should tell me this?
-I cannot unravel this secret without you.

00:08:20.758 --> 00:08:22.510 line:90%
I have no choice but to trust you.

00:08:23.011 --> 00:08:24.220 line:90%
Good grief.

00:08:25.054 --> 00:08:26.472 line:90%
What a life.

00:08:31.060 --> 00:08:32.478 line:90%
You should leave now.

00:08:39.110 --> 00:08:43.031 line:90%
We must uncover who the Most Favored Lady
of the Court really is. Get ready.

00:08:51.456 --> 00:08:54.000 line:90%
I went to the Queen Dowager's residence
to pay my respects,

00:08:54.500 --> 00:08:56.085 line:90%
and I saw Saeng-gang there.

00:08:57.170 --> 00:09:00.465 line:90%
She was dressed as a court lady
and with a strange man.

00:09:00.965 --> 00:09:03.301 line:90%
Did you give her
something dangerous to do?

00:09:03.384 --> 00:09:05.887 line:90%
You need not concern yourself with it.

00:09:07.180 --> 00:09:08.765 line:90%
Mother,

00:09:09.849 --> 00:09:12.852 line:90%
you need only concern yourself
with my son.

00:09:15.688 --> 00:09:16.898 line:90%
More importantly…

00:09:19.067 --> 00:09:22.487 line:90%
the Queen Dowager
is harboring ulterior motives.

00:09:27.033 --> 00:09:29.118 line:90%
It seems she intends

00:09:30.912 --> 00:09:33.664 line:90%
to make the eldest son of Prince Iksang
Crown Prince.

00:09:35.750 --> 00:09:37.085 line:90%
In any case,

00:09:38.002 --> 00:09:41.297 line:90%
we must act for the good
of the royal house and the nation.

00:10:00.316 --> 00:10:05.113 line:90%
You know what I had to endure to get here,

00:10:05.196 --> 00:10:07.365 line:90%
and yet you say such a thing to me?

00:10:08.991 --> 00:10:11.994 line:90%
Things will never go
as the Queen Dowager intends.

00:10:12.078 --> 00:10:14.330 line:90%
My son will inherit the throne.

00:10:14.414 --> 00:10:18.251 line:90%
Actually, I will make certain of it.

00:10:21.003 --> 00:10:22.213 line:90%
Yes.

00:10:24.340 --> 00:10:27.385 line:90%
Even if it means using spirits.

00:10:36.102 --> 00:10:39.439 line:90%
Why did we sneak into the chambers
of Lady Jang? We are not thieves.

00:10:41.691 --> 00:10:43.526 line:90%
Are you some kind of saint?

00:10:44.819 --> 00:10:47.655 line:90%
Lady Jang has spent her whole life
beside the Queen Dowager

00:10:47.738 --> 00:10:49.615 line:90%
and must know all her secrets.

00:10:50.116 --> 00:10:53.703 line:90%
So I mean to scare her into spilling
everything about the pond spirit.

00:10:54.745 --> 00:10:57.874 line:90%
Then do it properly.
What on earth are we doing?

00:10:59.000 --> 00:10:59.917 line:90%
Ma'am.

00:11:00.501 --> 00:11:02.670 line:90%
You are back earlier than usual.

00:11:02.753 --> 00:11:03.963 line:90%
I am not feeling well.

00:11:04.046 --> 00:11:05.047 line:90%
-I need rest.
-There!

00:11:05.131 --> 00:11:06.340 line:90%
This is bad.

00:11:10.219 --> 00:11:11.053 line:90%
Wait!

00:11:16.184 --> 00:11:17.852 line:90%
Who… who are you?

00:11:18.352 --> 00:11:20.188 line:90%
Who are you to enter without permission…

00:11:22.732 --> 00:11:24.150 line:90%
The pond spirit…

00:11:27.111 --> 00:11:30.740 line:90%
-The pond spirit is here.
-Wait, are you not that feng shui master?

00:11:30.823 --> 00:11:32.909 line:90%
-What are you doing here?
-Quiet!

00:11:34.494 --> 00:11:36.287 line:90%
-Look at these footprints on the floor.
-What…

00:11:39.415 --> 00:11:40.500 line:90%
Is this pond mud?

00:11:40.583 --> 00:11:41.959 line:90%
Leave at once!

00:11:42.043 --> 00:11:44.921 line:90%
-Or I will summon the guards.
-Wait. I can feel it.

00:11:45.004 --> 00:11:46.297 line:90%
The pond spirit…

00:11:46.839 --> 00:11:47.673 line:90%
What…

00:11:49.759 --> 00:11:50.801 line:90%
It is the pond spirit…

00:11:53.262 --> 00:11:55.723 line:90%
-Hey. You should earn your keep.
-You wretch!

00:11:55.806 --> 00:11:57.391 line:90%
Do what you are good at. Now.

00:11:57.475 --> 00:11:59.894 line:90%
-How dare you come in here!
-Hey. Hurry!

00:12:00.728 --> 00:12:02.647 line:90%
What do you think you are doing?

00:12:03.147 --> 00:12:06.609 line:90%
How dare <i>you </i>pull something so absurd!
Is anyone out there?

00:12:11.739 --> 00:12:14.033 line:90%
Where is that crying coming from…

00:12:14.116 --> 00:12:17.203 line:90%
I will wipe out every last seed
of the East Palace!

00:12:20.164 --> 00:12:23.292 line:90%
The pond spirit. It is here.

00:12:23.376 --> 00:12:26.254 line:90%
I told you
at the Queen Dowager's residence.

00:12:26.921 --> 00:12:30.091 line:90%
Won-gwi finds the one responsible
for its death…

00:13:05.626 --> 00:13:08.879 line:90%
Namo Amitabha.

00:13:11.757 --> 00:13:13.384 line:90%
Namo Amitabha.

00:13:13.968 --> 00:13:15.886 line:90%
You said you were a feng shui master.

00:13:17.888 --> 00:13:20.391 line:90%
Do you also know how to deal with spirits?

00:13:24.854 --> 00:13:26.355 line:90%
Speaking of which…

00:13:28.608 --> 00:13:30.359 line:90%
that damned spirit

00:13:31.986 --> 00:13:34.989 line:90%
will come for you again.

00:13:35.573 --> 00:13:36.657 line:90%
Again?

00:13:38.701 --> 00:13:40.745 line:90%
Then what should I do?

00:13:41.329 --> 00:13:43.873 line:90%
To keep the pond spirit away from here,

00:13:43.956 --> 00:13:48.753 line:90%
I need to know who it was in life.

00:13:50.504 --> 00:13:51.797 line:90%
Do not worry.

00:13:51.881 --> 00:13:54.133 line:90%
You can tell him everything you know.

00:13:54.634 --> 00:13:56.969 line:90%
He will keep it
from Her Majesty the Queen Dowager.

00:13:57.053 --> 00:13:59.096 line:90%
-He knows how to keep a secret.
-What?

00:14:02.099 --> 00:14:03.100 line:90%
Of course.

00:14:04.560 --> 00:14:05.561 line:90%
So,

00:14:07.229 --> 00:14:08.981 line:90%
who is the pond spirit?

00:14:11.192 --> 00:14:12.818 line:90%
The pond spirit is…

00:14:18.699 --> 00:14:23.871 line:90%
the last Most favored Lady of the Court
to the late King.

00:14:29.126 --> 00:14:32.421 line:90%
<i>A woman of the lowest birth,</i>
<i>a mere maidservant,</i>

00:14:32.922 --> 00:14:35.216 line:90%
<i>caught the eye of the late King.</i>

00:14:36.008 --> 00:14:39.845 line:90%
<i>She received favor of His Majesty</i>
<i>and even conceived.</i>

00:14:43.307 --> 00:14:46.060 line:90%
<i>But it turned out</i>

00:14:46.894 --> 00:14:50.815 line:90%
<i>that she was romantically involved</i>
<i>with a royal guard.</i>

00:14:53.984 --> 00:14:56.821 line:90%
<i>When Her Majesty the Queen Dowager</i>
<i>learned of this,</i>

00:14:58.698 --> 00:15:00.366 line:90%
<i>she had the royal guard tortured.</i>

00:15:00.449 --> 00:15:01.492 line:90%
Hold still!

00:15:02.326 --> 00:15:05.079 line:90%
<i>But he did not confess easily.</i>

00:15:06.997 --> 00:15:10.042 line:90%
<i>Troops were dispatched,</i>
<i>and they found evidence.</i>

00:15:10.876 --> 00:15:14.088 line:90%
<i>-He eventually admitted his guilt.</i>
-Go and search!

00:15:14.755 --> 00:15:16.674 line:90%
The Most Favored Lady of the Court

00:15:18.300 --> 00:15:22.388 line:90%
bore the child of the royal guard,
not of the late King.

00:15:22.972 --> 00:15:24.932 line:90%
After enduring torture,

00:15:25.433 --> 00:15:27.309 line:90%
she miscarried

00:15:27.935 --> 00:15:31.021 line:90%
and died holding a grudge
against the royal family.

00:15:31.522 --> 00:15:34.650 line:90%
I will wipe out every last seed
of the East Palace!

00:15:39.488 --> 00:15:43.242 line:90%
Then what happened to her body?

00:15:45.578 --> 00:15:47.747 line:90%
It was secretly taken out of the palace.

00:15:48.247 --> 00:15:50.458 line:90%
A grave would never have been an option.

00:15:51.375 --> 00:15:52.626 line:90%
What about her belongings?

00:15:53.669 --> 00:15:56.046 line:90%
They belonged to a traitor,
so they were all burned.

00:15:57.798 --> 00:16:00.259 line:90%
So there is nothing left of her?

00:16:04.054 --> 00:16:06.223 line:90%
I expect so. She had no family.

00:16:11.270 --> 00:16:14.732 line:90%
She died by her own wrongdoing
yet cursed the royal house?

00:16:16.692 --> 00:16:18.235 line:90%
There must be some greater reason,

00:16:18.736 --> 00:16:20.821 line:90%
involving the shameful secrets
of the palace.

00:16:23.783 --> 00:16:28.496 line:90%
I will have to ask the pond spirit myself.
Is there a way to summon it?

00:16:29.371 --> 00:16:30.790 line:90%
And what are you going to do?

00:16:30.873 --> 00:16:33.000 line:90%
There is no way to send it
to the afterlife.

00:16:39.089 --> 00:16:40.424 line:90%
Lady Jang said

00:16:41.091 --> 00:16:44.386 line:90%
everyone who entered the house
of the royal guard met an untimely death.

00:16:44.470 --> 00:16:47.598 line:90%
-Perhaps its spirit has settled there.
-Exactly.

00:16:48.098 --> 00:16:51.727 line:90%
There must be a reason he lingers
in that house instead of passing on.

00:16:52.228 --> 00:16:55.648 line:90%
Since they were lovers, the court lady
may have left her belongings behind.

00:16:56.899 --> 00:16:58.776 line:90%
I must go to the house of the royal guard.

00:16:58.859 --> 00:17:00.319 line:90%
Have you lost your mind?

00:17:01.362 --> 00:17:04.532 line:90%
-Do you want to die an untimely death?
-We have no other choice.

00:17:05.241 --> 00:17:07.785 line:90%
I am the only one
who can leave the palace.

00:17:07.868 --> 00:17:09.662 line:90%
There is a way.

00:17:10.287 --> 00:17:11.914 line:90%
I can become a soul and leave.

00:17:16.001 --> 00:17:18.754 line:90%
Is that even possible?

00:17:19.505 --> 00:17:21.173 line:90%
Yes, but it is dangerous.

00:17:22.258 --> 00:17:24.635 line:90%
If the soul drifts too far from the body…

00:17:27.096 --> 00:17:28.806 line:90%
it will be hard for it to return.

00:17:30.140 --> 00:17:31.141 line:90%
If things go wrong,

00:17:32.601 --> 00:17:34.311 line:90%
the soul may be lost…

00:17:36.689 --> 00:17:38.566 line:90%
and become a spirit.

00:17:41.235 --> 00:17:43.696 line:90%
If that happens,
I will surely become an ak-gwi.

00:17:43.779 --> 00:17:45.447 line:90%
Ak-gwi?

00:17:47.032 --> 00:17:50.160 line:90%
When those with heavy karma die,
they become an ak-gwi.

00:17:51.203 --> 00:17:52.413 line:90%
In life…

00:17:56.542 --> 00:17:57.835 line:90%
Are you all right?

00:18:03.549 --> 00:18:04.967 line:90%
Do you see something

00:18:06.010 --> 00:18:07.553 line:90%
in the well?

00:18:15.686 --> 00:18:17.605 line:90%
You do not look well.

00:18:18.272 --> 00:18:19.857 line:90%
If you need my Yang energy--

00:18:19.940 --> 00:18:24.278 line:90%
Then you would have to hold me close
and share your warmth.

00:18:24.361 --> 00:18:25.696 line:90%
Can you do that for me?

00:18:28.532 --> 00:18:31.493 line:90%
Never mind.
I have no intention of doing that either.

00:18:32.745 --> 00:18:34.330 line:90%
Then will you remain this way?

00:18:34.413 --> 00:18:36.540 line:90%
No, it will get worse.

00:18:36.624 --> 00:18:38.667 line:90%
Then from now on, I will accompany you

00:18:40.044 --> 00:18:41.587 line:90%
to the Realm of Gwi.

00:18:41.670 --> 00:18:43.380 line:90%
Two are better than one.

00:18:43.464 --> 00:18:44.924 line:90%
Teach me how.

00:18:47.092 --> 00:18:48.594 line:90%
Are you asking me

00:18:49.219 --> 00:18:51.972 line:90%
to teach you how to die?

00:18:52.056 --> 00:18:54.725 line:90%
I should find a way to help you.

00:18:54.808 --> 00:18:56.602 line:90%
There is only one way.

00:18:57.728 --> 00:18:59.605 line:90%
Go and tell the King

00:19:00.105 --> 00:19:02.983 line:90%
that there is no way
to catch the pond spirit now

00:19:03.484 --> 00:19:06.445 line:90%
and that I may lose control
and start killing people,

00:19:06.528 --> 00:19:08.405 line:90%
so he must release me from the palace.

00:19:13.953 --> 00:19:14.870 line:90%
I cannot do that.

00:19:16.121 --> 00:19:17.998 line:90%
You have to find a way.

00:19:18.082 --> 00:19:22.169 line:90%
Let go of the naive thought
that His Majesty will release you.

00:19:26.840 --> 00:19:29.468 line:90%
Then I will leave this palace in death.

00:19:34.974 --> 00:19:36.976 line:90%
If I die here,

00:19:38.310 --> 00:19:40.604 line:90%
I will turn into a relentless ak-gwi.

00:19:40.688 --> 00:19:42.356 line:90%
And when I do…

00:19:44.692 --> 00:19:46.986 line:90%
I will come for the King first.

00:19:49.405 --> 00:19:50.489 line:90%
How dare you

00:19:52.032 --> 00:19:54.493 line:90%
threaten to kill His Majesty.

00:19:54.576 --> 00:19:55.953 line:90%
What does it matter to you?

00:19:56.954 --> 00:19:58.664 line:90%
You hate the King as well.

00:19:58.747 --> 00:19:59.707 line:90%
I do.

00:19:59.790 --> 00:20:01.583 line:90%
Yet he is the King of this nation.

00:20:01.667 --> 00:20:04.336 line:90%
All royals are the same.

00:20:05.587 --> 00:20:07.673 line:90%
They use whoever they please

00:20:08.632 --> 00:20:11.385 line:90%
and do not even care
if people live or die.

00:20:13.762 --> 00:20:15.848 line:90%
You are no different.

00:20:21.478 --> 00:20:22.479 line:90%
Miss.

00:20:27.818 --> 00:20:30.279 line:90%
Royal Noble Consort Sukbin Choi
wishes to see you.

00:20:32.740 --> 00:20:34.950 line:90%
It has been a while, Grandmother.

00:20:35.034 --> 00:20:36.702 line:90%
His Majesty told me everything.

00:20:37.202 --> 00:20:40.914 line:90%
How could you think of disguising yourself
as a court lady to enter the palace?

00:20:41.415 --> 00:20:43.959 line:90%
And what brings you to the palace,
Grandmother?

00:20:44.043 --> 00:20:47.004 line:90%
You hated coming to the palace
more than anyone.

00:20:47.880 --> 00:20:51.300 line:90%
Will you not answer my question?
Same as always. You change the subject.

00:20:54.219 --> 00:20:55.471 line:90%
I am exhausted.

00:20:57.264 --> 00:20:59.016 line:90%
Oh dear.

00:21:02.853 --> 00:21:04.104 line:90%
Saeng-gang.

00:21:05.773 --> 00:21:09.026 line:90%
I hope you do not get caught up
in palace strife again,

00:21:09.109 --> 00:21:11.111 line:90%
as you did as a child.

00:21:13.781 --> 00:21:18.410 line:90%
You are the only one
who worries about me, Grandmother.

00:21:21.872 --> 00:21:24.291 line:90%
After Mother and I were driven
out of the palace,

00:21:25.292 --> 00:21:29.505 line:90%
there was no one but you
who took care of us.

00:21:30.756 --> 00:21:32.299 line:90%
What is that man like?

00:21:32.382 --> 00:21:35.177 line:90%
I have heard he is strange and dangerous.

00:21:37.638 --> 00:21:39.389 line:90%
He may be strange,

00:21:40.099 --> 00:21:42.392 line:90%
but he is the one I need most right now.

00:21:43.894 --> 00:21:45.646 line:90%
And he may be dangerous…

00:21:47.773 --> 00:21:49.858 line:90%
but I do not mind,
as we will not be friends.

00:21:53.362 --> 00:21:57.241 line:90%
The palace is a place
where the sane become ill,

00:21:57.908 --> 00:22:01.578 line:90%
and those with darkness in their hearts
become evil.

00:22:03.705 --> 00:22:05.499 line:90%
So you must be careful.

00:22:16.343 --> 00:22:17.678 line:90%
<i>Gu-cheon.</i>

00:22:28.605 --> 00:22:30.566 line:90%
<i>You have missed me, have you not?</i>

00:22:33.152 --> 00:22:35.445 line:90%
<i>Come here.</i>

00:22:54.089 --> 00:22:55.215 line:90%
This is strange.

00:22:55.716 --> 00:22:59.136 line:90%
People died here before.
That is why the well was sealed.

00:22:59.219 --> 00:23:00.804 line:90%
And another maidservant died?

00:23:00.888 --> 00:23:06.185 line:90%
Earlier at dawn, a maidservant saw a man
near the well while carrying wash water.

00:23:06.268 --> 00:23:08.228 line:90%
-Is that so?
-Yes.

00:23:08.312 --> 00:23:11.481 line:90%
It was the feng shui master
staying at the East Palace.

00:23:12.274 --> 00:23:14.568 line:90%
Shall I send him to the State Tribunal?

00:23:14.651 --> 00:23:17.237 line:90%
No. The 70th birthday
of the Queen Dowager is near.

00:23:17.321 --> 00:23:19.114 line:90%
This must be handled discreetly.

00:23:19.781 --> 00:23:21.408 line:90%
We must not cause a disturbance.

00:23:21.909 --> 00:23:23.118 line:90%
-Yes, ma'am.
-Yes, ma'am.

00:23:53.232 --> 00:23:54.316 line:90%
Gu-cheon.

00:24:02.950 --> 00:24:04.451 line:90%
What is this bloodstain?

00:24:08.080 --> 00:24:09.414 line:90%
What is this?

00:24:10.582 --> 00:24:13.043 line:90%
What are you doing out at night?

00:24:13.627 --> 00:24:15.337 line:90%
Whose blood is this?

00:24:16.505 --> 00:24:17.923 line:90%
What do you mean "whose blood"?

00:24:20.592 --> 00:24:22.302 line:90%
Are you saying I harmed someone?

00:24:26.056 --> 00:24:27.724 line:90%
Then is it your blood?

00:24:28.976 --> 00:24:31.561 line:90%
Where were you hurt? And why?

00:24:31.645 --> 00:24:34.022 line:90%
Perhaps I had a nosebleed in my sleep.

00:24:35.607 --> 00:24:37.609 line:90%
After fighting the court ladies' spirits,

00:24:38.360 --> 00:24:39.778 line:90%
I barely had any strength left.

00:24:40.612 --> 00:24:43.365 line:90%
Even that damned Ggeomeoksali
kept draining my Yang energy.

00:24:46.743 --> 00:24:48.287 line:90%
I already told you

00:24:48.370 --> 00:24:51.290 line:90%
that every time I enter the Realm of Gwi,
I lose my Yang energy.

00:25:20.319 --> 00:25:21.403 line:90%
Prince Yeongan.

00:25:23.780 --> 00:25:25.574 line:90%
You need to get your strength back.

00:25:26.074 --> 00:25:27.993 line:90%
It was not this severe before,

00:25:28.493 --> 00:25:31.580 line:90%
but his condition suddenly worsened.

00:26:05.113 --> 00:26:06.490 line:90%
Coming back to the East Palace

00:26:07.866 --> 00:26:11.036 line:90%
reminds me of my childhood here.

00:26:12.621 --> 00:26:15.248 line:90%
This place still gives me chills.

00:26:16.625 --> 00:26:19.503 line:90%
What brings you here,
to a place you find so chilling?

00:26:22.214 --> 00:26:24.716 line:90%
How much longer do I have to wait?

00:26:25.509 --> 00:26:27.636 line:90%
I came to hear your answer myself.

00:26:27.719 --> 00:26:30.055 line:90%
First, please let me leave the palace.

00:26:30.138 --> 00:26:31.473 line:90%
If I stay here any longer,

00:26:32.057 --> 00:26:34.601 line:90%
the Yin energy of this place will kill me.

00:26:35.769 --> 00:26:37.437 line:90%
If you let me leave,

00:26:37.521 --> 00:26:40.065 line:90%
I will capture the pond spirit
no matter what.

00:26:43.735 --> 00:26:46.905 line:90%
Tomorrow is the 70th birthday banquet
of the Queen Dowager.

00:26:48.365 --> 00:26:51.785 line:90%
Eliminate the pond spirit
and bring Prince Yeongan back to health.

00:26:52.285 --> 00:26:53.620 line:90%
You have until noon tomorrow.

00:26:55.580 --> 00:26:58.125 line:90%
-Your Majesty.
-Your life is no concern of mine.

00:26:59.167 --> 00:27:03.046 line:90%
You will not leave this palace
until I die.

00:27:04.089 --> 00:27:09.636 line:90%
If my son cannot walk into the banquet
on his own two feet tomorrow,

00:27:09.719 --> 00:27:12.806 line:90%
I will kill you
and bind your soul to the palace forever.

00:27:12.889 --> 00:27:14.349 line:90%
Do you understand?

00:27:15.517 --> 00:27:16.977 line:90%
Do you understand?

00:27:46.506 --> 00:27:49.676 line:90%
Wait, are you not the feng shui master
staying in the East Palace?

00:27:50.177 --> 00:27:52.262 line:90%
Why are you here?
This place is for women only.

00:27:54.014 --> 00:27:55.474 line:90%
-Where is she?
-What?

00:27:56.183 --> 00:27:58.226 line:90%
I may be young, but I am a court lady.

00:27:58.310 --> 00:27:59.895 line:90%
Watch how you speak to me.

00:27:59.978 --> 00:28:00.979 line:90%
This will not do.

00:28:01.062 --> 00:28:04.316 line:90%
-You must help me.
-What? That man dares…

00:28:04.983 --> 00:28:07.652 line:90%
Miss Saeng-gang gave the order. Follow me.

00:28:19.664 --> 00:28:20.874 line:90%
What is he doing?

00:28:25.545 --> 00:28:27.005 line:90%
What on earth are you doing?

00:28:42.354 --> 00:28:45.106 line:90%
What exactly did Miss Saeng-gang
order you to do?

00:28:45.857 --> 00:28:46.900 line:90%
<i>Place this brass basin</i>

00:28:46.983 --> 00:28:49.236 line:90%
<i>near the house of the royal guard</i>
<i>in Jungchon.</i>

00:28:50.612 --> 00:28:51.696 line:90%
<i>Mark my words.</i>

00:28:52.572 --> 00:28:54.824 line:90%
<i>You must never spill this water.</i>

00:28:57.327 --> 00:28:58.995 line:90%
<i>I have no choice but to use my blood…</i>

00:29:00.997 --> 00:29:03.458 line:90%
<i>become a soul,</i>
<i>and seek out the royal guard.</i>

00:29:19.641 --> 00:29:21.017 line:90%
What is going on?

00:29:21.601 --> 00:29:24.896 line:90%
It seems the lightning
struck the jujube tree.

00:29:24.980 --> 00:29:25.939 line:90%
An ill omen.

00:29:26.022 --> 00:29:29.985 line:90%
It is the 70th birthday of Her Majesty.
What a calamity.

00:29:30.485 --> 00:29:31.403 line:90%
Good heavens.

00:29:32.988 --> 00:29:34.990 line:90%
Ever heard of
lightning-struck jujube wood?

00:29:35.824 --> 00:29:36.741 line:90%
No, I have not.

00:29:37.242 --> 00:29:40.620 line:90%
More importantly, every peach tree
in the palace will be gone at this rate.

00:29:41.580 --> 00:29:43.832 line:90%
That is why I asked.

00:29:43.915 --> 00:29:47.127 line:90%
This wood rots when it strikes a spirit,
so it is utterly useless.

00:29:47.210 --> 00:29:50.297 line:90%
Is lightning-struck jujube wood
any different?

00:29:50.380 --> 00:29:52.424 line:90%
A jujube tree struck by lightning

00:29:52.507 --> 00:29:54.968 line:90%
is sturdy and dense enough
to sink as I do.

00:29:59.848 --> 00:30:02.809 line:90%
<i>It drives away evil spirits.</i>
<i>Perfect for striking them down.</i>

00:30:05.353 --> 00:30:06.521 line:90%
<i>Heaven is on our side.</i>

00:30:16.072 --> 00:30:17.782 line:90%
This man…

00:30:32.505 --> 00:30:33.798 line:90%
This is exhausting.

00:31:05.830 --> 00:31:06.873 line:90%
You…

00:31:07.874 --> 00:31:11.670 line:90%
You cannot…

00:31:19.344 --> 00:31:23.264 line:90%
You cannot take it.

00:33:30.975 --> 00:33:31.851 line:90%
Stop it!

00:33:35.021 --> 00:33:37.440 line:90%
What are you trying to protect,
even in death?

00:33:37.524 --> 00:33:38.983 line:90%
The fault is mine.

00:33:39.567 --> 00:33:41.903 line:90%
I must return it.

00:33:44.405 --> 00:33:46.699 line:90%
The fault is mine.

00:33:50.370 --> 00:33:52.997 line:90%
I killed her!

00:33:59.087 --> 00:34:00.797 line:90%
<i>Your blood is on this sword.</i>

00:34:00.880 --> 00:34:01.840 line:90%
<i>Take it.</i>

00:34:57.645 --> 00:34:58.855 line:90%
I killed her.

00:35:00.106 --> 00:35:02.692 line:90%
After she became a woman of the King,

00:35:02.775 --> 00:35:04.277 line:90%
I framed her

00:35:05.403 --> 00:35:07.155 line:90%
and betrayed her.

00:35:11.200 --> 00:35:12.785 line:90%
<i>In return for doing so,</i>

00:35:13.494 --> 00:35:16.748 line:90%
<i>for making a false confession,</i>

00:35:17.248 --> 00:35:18.499 line:90%
<i>the Queen Dowager promised</i>

00:35:19.334 --> 00:35:24.172 line:90%
<i>to spare my family from annihilation.</i>

00:35:30.219 --> 00:35:31.179 line:90%
<i>She had made</i>

00:35:32.055 --> 00:35:36.017 line:90%
<i>the baby's first shirt with all her heart</i>…

00:35:40.063 --> 00:35:43.483 line:90%
and I buried it beneath this tree.

00:35:49.822 --> 00:35:50.823 line:90%
I must

00:35:51.324 --> 00:35:53.368 line:90%
protect it

00:35:53.451 --> 00:35:55.578 line:90%
until she returns.

00:35:58.748 --> 00:35:59.874 line:90%
<i>I must beg</i>

00:36:01.084 --> 00:36:03.461 line:90%
<i>her forgiveness.</i>

00:36:50.008 --> 00:36:51.467 line:90%
What are you trying to do?

00:36:52.760 --> 00:36:54.637 line:90%
Wait! Miss Saeng-gang!

00:37:03.062 --> 00:37:04.647 line:90%
Gu-cheon!

00:37:07.316 --> 00:37:09.068 line:90%
Is he alive?

00:37:10.570 --> 00:37:13.322 line:90%
This madman entered the Realm of Gwi
without the rope.

00:37:13.406 --> 00:37:15.074 line:90%
I cannot even pull his soul back.

00:37:15.575 --> 00:37:16.576 line:90%
Look.

00:37:16.659 --> 00:37:17.910 line:90%
Where are you now?

00:37:17.994 --> 00:37:20.329 line:90%
Look. Gu-cheon!

00:37:20.413 --> 00:37:21.914 line:90%
Are you even on your way back?

00:37:54.489 --> 00:37:56.908 line:90%
<i>If the soul drifts too far from the body,</i>

00:37:56.991 --> 00:37:58.785 line:90%
<i>it will be hard for it to return.</i>

00:37:58.868 --> 00:38:04.624 line:90%
-Wake up, Gu-cheon!
<i>-The soul may be lost and become a spirit.</i>

00:38:06.334 --> 00:38:09.212 line:90%
<i>If that happens,</i>
<i>I will surely become an ak-gwi.</i>

00:38:14.300 --> 00:38:17.470 line:90%
<i>I will not let you wander alone</i>
<i>as a spirit.</i>

00:38:18.554 --> 00:38:21.724 line:90%
<i>I will come to you.</i>

00:38:22.683 --> 00:38:24.060 line:90%
<i>Please wait for me.</i>

00:38:24.727 --> 00:38:25.812 line:90%
<i>Please.</i>

00:39:50.771 --> 00:39:51.606 line:90%
Gu-cheon.

00:39:57.904 --> 00:39:59.447 line:90%
Come here.

00:40:10.499 --> 00:40:11.417 line:90%
Come here.

00:40:12.627 --> 00:40:13.711 line:90%
Mother.

00:40:18.299 --> 00:40:19.258 line:90%
Gu-cheon!

00:40:21.135 --> 00:40:22.553 line:90%
Do not go any closer!

00:40:22.637 --> 00:40:24.805 line:90%
-Gu-cheon.
-Let us leave this place.

00:40:24.889 --> 00:40:27.183 line:90%
That gwi-mae lures people to their deaths.

00:40:27.266 --> 00:40:29.518 line:90%
-You missed me, did you not?
-Gu-cheon!

00:40:30.561 --> 00:40:32.647 line:90%
-Please look properly!
-Come here.

00:40:35.316 --> 00:40:36.400 line:90%
Mother.

00:40:37.485 --> 00:40:38.486 line:90%
Gu-cheon!

00:41:08.891 --> 00:41:09.725 line:90%
<i>Mother.</i>

00:41:27.868 --> 00:41:28.869 line:90%
Mother.

00:41:32.623 --> 00:41:33.624 line:90%
<i>Mother.</i>

00:41:37.211 --> 00:41:39.380 line:90%
I died because of you.

00:41:44.552 --> 00:41:45.594 line:90%
Let go of me.

00:43:00.419 --> 00:43:01.504 line:90%
Gu-cheon!

00:43:10.429 --> 00:43:13.099 line:90%
Then I will leave this palace in death.

00:43:15.017 --> 00:43:16.977 line:90%
If I die here,

00:43:17.728 --> 00:43:19.939 line:90%
I will turn into a relentless ak-gwi.

00:43:20.022 --> 00:43:21.690 line:90%
And when I do…

00:43:23.984 --> 00:43:25.986 line:90%
I will come for the King first.

00:43:27.488 --> 00:43:28.697 line:90%
Could he be…

00:47:16.800 --> 00:47:20.095 line:90%
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang